{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 3271799, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "NellieBly", "body": "A Shadowlands question about Uniting the Broken Isles.. we want to do this quest, and chased around Dalaran for a while after not finding Khadgar in Violet Citadel, Krasus Landing (his usual stomping grounds)... then finally realised that we are most likely in a wrong version of Dalaran.   So how does one get to the right one, the Broken Isles verion, not Crystalsong?   Is it possible to take part in the moving of dalaran?   That would be a plus    [quest=43341 domain=www]   Thanks !", "date": "2020-12-10T16:43:20-06:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I did the same thing! I went back to Stormwind and took the portal in the opposite hallway to Azsuna. From there I flew (or go to the nearest flight point) to Dalaran. The quest was right there after that!", "creationdate": "2020-12-12T22:20:24-06:00", "id": 1425207, "rating": 5, "commentid": 3271799, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "KatTheDark", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
