{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 2380795, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Extrawesome", "body": "UNABLE TO START THE LEGION QUESTLINE? Khadgar's Upgraded Servant Bugged? Dropped the quest and can't get it back? **Solved!**\n\nThere is an NPC for each faction:\nHorde: [url=npc=4311]Holgar Stormaxe[/url]\nAlliance: [url=npc=107934]Recruiter Lee[/url] [small][b]*See edit at bottom*[/b][/small]\nthat will get you where you need to go.\n\nSimply interact with them and select this[url=https://i.imgur.com/TlUAR0J.png] dialog option[/url] , accept the confirmation [url=https://i.imgur.com/v7MI4lJ.png]pop-up[/url] . You will be given the quest [url=quest=44184]In the Blink of an Eye[/url] and teleported directly to New Dalaran where you can start your Artifact Quest and thus the Expansion. Win!\n\nI have been looking all over for information on this issue and there has been little to be found anywhere, so I thought i'd post here in hopes that it saves other adventurers some time that ought be spent playing!\n------------------\n[b]Edit: [/b]Alliance seems to be having some other technical issues that this might not solve.", "date": "2016-09-01T15:57:23-05:00", "rating": 13, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "not working here :( no dialog option appears", "creationdate": "2016-09-01T20:45:11-05:00", "id": 965998, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2380795, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "paulosales123", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "i was able to do this on my alts, but he seems persistent in following me on them :/", "creationdate": "2016-09-06T13:25:06-05:00", "id": 970025, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2380795, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Nieniin", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Not receiving the quest In the Blink of an Eye in 8.1", "creationdate": "2018-12-19T14:40:18-06:00", "id": 1210827, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2380795, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Noctemus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Same. I even did the intro to BFA in case the harbour instance interfere with Legion quests. Elerion Bladedancer cannot be interacted with after handing in Illidari Allies and neither Recruiter Lee nor Khadgar's Upgraded Servant can be found anywhere.", "creationdate": "2018-12-24T09:54:27-06:00", "id": 1211670, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2380795, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "akkmok", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-09-01T20:08:26-05:00", 1, "Extrawesome"]}
