{"commentv2": 1, "number": 8, "id": 2394388, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Villainess", "body": "For anyone else who has had trouble ditching this annoying guy, there was a blue post several days ago with a workaround; If you go to the new Dalaran (in the Broken Isles) and talk to Archivist Elysiana in the Violet Citadel, she will allow you to redo the pre-launch quest over Deadwind Pass. (Just vanquish some anomalies and talk to Khadgar.) This fulfills the purpose of Khadgar's servant and he'll no longer be a nuisance. \r\n\r\nAfter completing the quest, I can confidently say I am stalker free. [i]FINALLY.[/i]", "date": "2016-09-09T15:28:29-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "http://www.wowhead.com/npc=113873/archivist-elysiana", "creationdate": "2016-09-09T21:22:55-05:00", "id": 973564, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2394388, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Rispetto", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
