{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2063368, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Higgi", "body": "Fun Fact for the day, Khadgar is voiced by Tony Amendola, Master Bra'tac from Stargate SG-1", "date": "2014-12-08T05:20:11-06:00", "rating": 25, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Maybe I'm being a silly fangirl who is mesmerized by how much of a silver fox he is after the shave and a haircut, but I think Tony Amendola's voice is a bit too old for Khadgar. The voice actor is in his 70s, and Khadgar is in his mid 40s. I also recall that the curse really only effected his face and hair, but he otherwise still felt young. (I dunno. Like I said... I'm being silly)", "creationdate": "2014-12-12T13:04:09-06:00", "id": 811628, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2063368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Ayrianna", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I think his voice is great with the character. What was sad was hearing and seeing Stinky Pete the Prospector being voiced by Kelsey Grammer.", "creationdate": "2015-01-03T20:03:38-06:00", "id": 822848, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2063368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "HIGHERGROUND", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Khadgar speaks to Alliance and Horde forces after picking up Gul'dan's dagger from Gul'dan's corpse at the end of the legendary questline: \"This single blade did what we could not - it has brought us together. This blade has spilled the blood of the Alliance, and of the Horde. By the hand of our common enemy, it has made us brothers. Together, we have ensured that it will never spill our blood again!\" https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5kOjZ2kWI3A SHEL KEK NEM RON! BRA'TAC-VOICED KHADGAR LED US THRU THE PORTAL! PRAISE SPACE MOSES! SPACE MOSES AND GREEN JESUS DELIVERED US TO THE PROMISED GARRISON!", "creationdate": "2015-01-07T08:17:39-06:00", "id": 824573, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2063368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "cwmatt11", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "@Ayrianna If you're being aged magically, I imagine it affects your whole body, just like natural aging does, not that I know for sure though. Thus, imo the voice fits him just fine. Also his new model is really nice.", "creationdate": "2015-01-14T02:12:08-06:00", "id": 827695, "rating": 4, "commentid": 2063368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ringabell", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Tek Mate master Khadgar.", "creationdate": "2017-10-02T02:34:20-05:00", "id": 1077906, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2063368, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "TamiayTheGnome", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2068591, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "runtimemess", "body": "Is it just me or is Khadgar's art style really out of place compared to the other main characters in this expansion? (Thrall, etc....)", "date": "2014-12-14T03:14:44-06:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I think it's just you. I feel like the main characters represent different environments and themes of the expansion. Thrall put on his armor again and is off to see his papa and mama. Then there's Maraad and Yrel representing the draenei and being total badasses on the side. And above all, there's Khadgar tying it all together. Personally, I questioned Cordana Felsong - she seems to have no story or background whatsoever. Also, having the same model as Maiev is bound to result in confusion. (Not to mention that the model itself is awfully old and really feels out of place, imo)", "creationdate": "2015-01-14T02:20:36-06:00", "id": 827697, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2068591, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ringabell", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 2084846, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Skullhawk13", "body": "Khadgar is such a badass. He'd easily solo the content himself, but merely lets the player do his work for him, to not deprive them of the loot.", "date": "2015-01-08T10:50:54-06:00", "rating": 13, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Or like all badasses, they get other people to do their work for them!", "creationdate": "2015-01-08T14:03:56-06:00", "id": 825168, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2084846, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "etherealmist", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "His MO is basically, \"I've got this, until I don't... But then I've got you\"", "creationdate": "2015-01-11T18:59:40-06:00", "id": 826758, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2084846, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Ayrianna", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
