{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 124658, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Russius", "body": "To get the tour quest from Khadgar, you must speak to the Haggard War Veteran at 59,40 in Shattrath.  This will send you to A'dal.  Talk to him, then Khadgar will tell you to leave him alone.  Then you can get the tour quest from Khadgar, which allows you to build rep with Aldor/Scryer.  Follow Khadgar's elemental servant around until you get a quest completion.  No, you can't /follow.\n\nWhat a pain that was to find...", "date": "2007-07-21T18:54:34-05:00", "rating": 22, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "just thought that i'd point out - the haggard war veteran quest isn't required as pre-requisite to take the the tour from Khadgar. at level 60 you can speak to him straight away.  The tour quest we speak of can be found here: \t[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10211]City of Light[/url]", "creationdate": "2007-11-14T14:45:25-06:00", "id": 18768, "rating": 3, "commentid": 124658, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Hirotoro", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Please read discussion at [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10211]City of Light[/url] as there seems to be some confusion as to whom tells you to speak to whom ( [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10210]A`dal[/url] ), and after you've done what.  At least that's the only way I can comprehend my comment getting rated down and purged.", "creationdate": "2008-01-26T20:11:58-06:00", "id": 24165, "rating": 5, "commentid": 124658, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Russius", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "OMG, finally, THANK YOU! I was going nuts trying to figure out how to join a damned faction in Shattrah.", "creationdate": "201