{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 372755, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "138326", "body": "Here is some Lore:\r\nKhadgar is a human mage that was from a apprentice from Medvih. In the Warcraft book \"Beyond the Dark portal\" he had helped Alleria Windrunner and Turalyon  stop Nerzhul from opening portals to other worlds in Outland. His job was to recover the skull of Gu'ldan from the dragon Deathwing, which he succedes in. Although Deathwing swore he will kill Khadgar one day, it has not occurred in Warcraft history......[yet]", "date": "2008-09-09T19:53:32-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The thing that I wrote down was made by myself, not from wowwiki (although I do believe I should have.) This is from what I read in the book \"Beyond the Dark Portal\"", "creationdate": "2009-01-21T21:44:17-06:00", "id": 74481, "rating": 2, "commentid": 372755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "138326", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "We just KILLED Deathwing! Khadgar shall live forever!!!", "creationdate": "2012-04-26T16:11:48-05:00", "id": 538937, "rating": 4, "commentid": 372755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "schaferjsbdja", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
