{"commentv2": 1, "number": 29, "id": 2024183, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Neza1337", "body": "Is the Khadgar that is present in Outland the same Khadgar that we meet in Draenor, or do we meet the younger Khadgar from the other timeline in WoD? Or have they now placed the model of Khadgar as 30 years younger from Draenor into our timeline in Shattrath?", "date": "2014-11-04T05:37:44-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "There is only Khadgar- the one from Outland. No he is not younger. His old model was just generic \"old human\". His current is unique.", "creationdate": "2014-11-05T06:51:11-06:00", "id": 786133, "rating": 7, "commentid": 2024183, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Combine456", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Apparently he is the younger version, though he's also in an alternate timeline. This quest text sheds a tiny bit of light on it: [quest=35350], \"Laara told me that they have Banthar here! Or rather, that she's still alive back now.\"", "creationdate": "2015-07-27T02:33:43-05:00", "id": 887685, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2024183, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Eido", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
