{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 1976975, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Stealthfire13", "body": "If you talk to him, it'll say:\n[quote]<The amorphous blob of arcane energy appears to be giving people a tour of your garrison.>[/quote]\nHe seems to be giving said tour so slowly that he appears to be standing still--which, naturally, is 100% accurate to [url=http://wod.wowhead.com/quest=10211]his behavior in Shattrath[/url].\n\nEdit: This was originally posted during beta when this guy literally just stood still in your garrison, 24/7. He now actually moves around while a few garrison NPCs follow him...at, naturally, a glacial pace.", "date": "2014-07-02T00:45:37-05:00", "rating": 78, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2015-03-10T04:05:30-05:00", 1, "Stealthfire13"]}
