{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2031477, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Eilonthay", "body": "When first picking up the quest in someplace other than the Blasted Lands, e.g. the Shrine of Seven Stars, the quest dialogue is as follows:\n\n[quote]<The archmage focuses intently on the portal.>\n\nLook.  Their numbers are abating, however briefly.  This may be our chance.\n\nAre you prepared to face whatever's on the other side of that portal?\n\nFOR AZEROTH![/quote]\n\nWhen you click on it, a dialogue box opens up:\n\n[quote]You are about to embark on a dangerous mission, and you may not be able to return immediately.  Are you sure?[/quote]\n\nHit \"accept\" and you'll be teleported directly to Draenor.  Keep your arms and legs inside at all times and don't trip!", "date": "2014-11-15T00:47:36-06:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2014-11-15T01:12:59-06:00", 1, "Eilonthay"]}
