{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2567684, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "sno4270", "body": "Came across this portal at 80,26, near Zangarra flight path. After you use it, you turn into what I am assuming is an arcane energy form and fly to Khadgar's Tower area. Once landed, there is another of these portals to take you back to the Zangarra flight path area.\r\n\r\nNot sure if this information is a duh to some people, but as I had not yet been questing much in the this area aside from setting up the Voljin's pride outpost somewhat, wasn't sure what to make of it. I was worried clicking it would take me and strand me far away from where I wanted to be.\r\n\r\nOnly reason I was in the area was trying to get the Zangarra flight path on my way to do a fishing daily.", "date": "2018-05-15T22:25:37-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "If you are wondering how the heck you get down to the mushrooms, this portal is how. Thank you for this post! I agree, so far most of the tasks that whisk you away in Draenor take you very far away! I came looking just for this information.", "creationdate": "2020-06-12T22:54:00-05:00", "id": 1374441, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2567684, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Bunne", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
