{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2372266, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "unholydriver", "body": "This NPC is in the scenario The Archmage during the quest [quest=40755]. He walks with [npc=101276] while Khadgar reflects on the fist time he entered Karazhan. The conversation between [npc=101285], [npc=101276] and [npc=101281] is as follows:\n\n[npc=101276]:  Care to borrow some blinders? Other students have found them quite helpful for ignoring those distracting visions. \n[npc=101281]:  Uh.. no, thank you. If I may ask, what became of the other students?\n[npc=101285]: So... It seems our young spy has arrived at last.", "date": "2016-08-22T18:12:38-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-08-31T07:29:56-05:00", 2, "unholydriver"]}
